    "The <b>Gravitation Potion</b> is a <linked>buff potion</linked> which grants the <b>Gravitation</b> <linked>buff</linked> when consumed. This buff allows the player to invert gravity with <span class=\"key\"><linked>▲ Up</linked></span> making the screen appear upside-down, fall upwards, and walk on top of the ceilings. The effect can be toggled while in midair. This lasts for 3 minutes, but can be canceled at any time  by right-clicking the icon (<linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked>),  by selecting the icon using Cycle Next/Previous Buff and then pressing Remove Buff (<linked>[img:Console version]</linked>),  by selecting the icon and canceling it in the equipment menu (<linked>[img:Old-gen console version]</linked>),  by double-tapping the buff icon (<linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked>), or  by canceling the buff from the buffs screen (<linked>[img:Nintendo 3DS version]</linked>)."
